<paragraph blockId="21.[120,1224,1599,1737]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">REFERRED SPECIMENS: NMT.014/Bat, right distal humerus, FLK N1, layer 3, no. 4; NMT.028/Bat, right distal humerus, FLK NNI, layer 2; NMT.029/Bat, left complete humerus, FLK NNI, layer 2; NMT.033/Bat, left distal humerus, FLK NI, layer 3, Tr. III (see table 1 for measurements).</paragraph>
